<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <title>구글 캘린더 연동 실패</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .error-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 40px 40px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .error-header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="dots" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23dots)"/></svg>');
    }
    
    .error-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: shake 1s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes shake {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
      25% {
        transform: translateX(-5px);
      }
      75% {
        transform: translateX(5px);
      }
    }
    
    .error-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .error-subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    
    .message {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .error-details {
      background: #fff5f5;
      border: 1px solid #feb2b2;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .error-details h3 {
      color: #c53030;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .error-reason {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #742a2a;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .troubleshooting {
      background: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .troubleshooting h3 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .step-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
    
    .step-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .step-number {
      background: #4285f4;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 12px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    
    .actions {
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 8px;
      min-width: 200px;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4 0%, #34a853 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: #6c757d;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #5a6268;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .footer-text {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
      }
      
      .error-header {
        padding: 40px 20px 30px;
      }
      
      .error-icon {
        font-size: 60px;
      }
      
      .error-title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .btn {
        min-width: auto;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="error-header">
      <div class="error-icon">😞</div>
      <h1 class="error-title">연동 실패</h1>
      <p class="error-subtitle">구글 캘린더 연동 중 문제가 발생했습니다</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p class="message">
        연동 과정에서 오류가 발생했습니다.<br>
        아래 방법을 시도해보세요.
      </p>
      
      <div class="error-details">
        <h3>🚨 발생한 문제</h3>
        <div class="error-reason">
          구글 인증 과정에서 오류가 발생했거나, 권한 승인이 취소되었을 수 있습니다.
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="troubleshooting">
        <h3>🔧 해결 방법</h3>
        <div class="step-item">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <span>브라우저의 쿠키와 캐시를 삭제해보세요</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <span>구글 계정에 로그인이 되어있는지 확인하세요</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <span>팝업 차단이 설정되어 있지 않은지 확인하세요</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <span class="step-number">4</span>
          <span>구글 캘린더 접근 권한을 허용했는지 확인하세요</span>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <span class="step-number">5</span>
          <span>잠시 후 다시 시도해보세요</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="actions">
        <% if (typeof token !== 'undefined' && token) { %>
          <a href="/googleauth?token=<%= token %>" class="btn btn-primary">
            🔄 다시 시도
          </a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-primary">
            🔄 다시 시도
          </a>
        <% } %>
        <a href="slack://open" class="btn btn-secondary">
          💬 슬랙으로 돌아가기
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p class="footer-text">
        문제가 계속 발생하면 관리자에게 문의해주세요
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // 페이지 로드 시 애니메이션
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const container = document.querySelector('.container');
      container.style.opacity = '0';
      container.style.transform = 'scale(0.9) translateY(20px)';
      
      setTimeout(() => {
        container.style.transition = 'all 0.6s ease';
        container.style.opacity = '1';
        container.style.transform = 'scale(1) translateY(0)';
      }, 100);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html> 